WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Eat to win the day. Here's a simple diabetic day, plate by plate.

00:07.000 --> 00:17.000
Start with the plate method. Half non-starchy veggies, a quarter lean protein, a quarter smart carbs.

00:17.000 --> 00:25.000
Breakfast: a veggie omelet, Greek yogurt, berries, and a few nuts.

00:25.000 --> 00:33.000
Lunch: a big salad with grilled chicken, olive oil, and chickpeas.

00:33.000 --> 00:41.000
Dinner: salmon, roasted vegetables, and a quarter-plate of quinoa.

00:41.000 --> 00:51.000
Prep once, win all week. Batch overnight oats, chopped veg, hard-boiled eggs, and portioned nuts.

00:51.000 --> 00:59.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:59.000 --> 01:05.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
